    "Similarly, the squared values of the correlation between constructs are also considerably below the AVE values of each construct.",
    "As a result, it can be concluded that the construct exhibits discriminant validity.The figures presented in Table 4 provide a comprehensive summary of the confirmatory factor analysis conducted.",
